Begin: Reorder Scan Chains

Usage: scanReorder [-help] [-addScanPortPrefix <value>]
                   [-clkAware {true|false}] [-preferH {true|false}]
                   [-preferV {true|false}] [-keepPDPorts {true|false} ] [-scanEffort {low|medium|high|auto} ] [-skipMode {skipNone|skipBuffer} ]

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
-addScanPortPrefix <value>             # prefix of scan hport (list, optional)
-clkAware {true|false}                 # specify whether scan reordering is
                                       # clock tree aware (bool, optional)
-keepPDPorts {true|false}              # maintains or corrects the hierarchical
                                       # ports without deleting or inserting
                                       # shifters, and reorders the remaining
                                       # scan chain (bool, optional)
-preferH {true|false}                  # makes horizontal scan chain
                                       # connections if possible (bool, optional)
-preferV {true|false}                  # makes vertical scan chain connections
                                       # if possible (bool, optional)
-scanEffort {low medium high auto}     # effort level (enum, optional)
-skipMode {skipNone skipBuffer}        # skip mode (enum, optional)